import React from 'react' import PropTypes from 'prop-types' import './' export const MessageHistory = ({msg}) => { if (!msg){return null} return msg.map((row,i)=>(< div key={i} className="message-history mt-3">
{row.messageBy}
{row.date}
{row.message}
)) } MessageHistory.propTypes={ msg:PropTypes.array.isRequired }
